### WAVE 1: Color & Typography Foundation
- [ ] Update CSS variables (index.css colors)
- [ ] Change font-family from 'Space Grotesk' to 'Inter' or 'system-ui'
- [ ] Update scrollbar colors to light theme
- [ ] Remove/update all gradient text styles
- [ ] Remove animation classes (matrix-column, gradientShift, float)
- [ ] Update .glass-card to solid background + shadow

