## Specific File Changes

### index.css
- Update CSS variable colors (light theme)
- REMOVE: @keyframes matrix-column, gradientShift, float
- REMOVE: .dot-grid, .gradient-text, .gradient-border, .glass-card
- ADD: Simple card shadow styles
- Update base body background to light
- Update scrollbar to light theme colors

### All .jsx components
- Remove className="gradient-text" from H1/H2
- Remove className="glass-card"
- Remove className="dot-grid"
- Remove animated background elements
- Update color references (primary/accent)
- Simplify animations to hover effects only

## Success Criteria
- [ ] No dark theme visible
- [ ] No gradient text effects
- [ ] No matrix/dot grid animations
- [ ] No glass/blur effects
- [ ] Typography reads clearly (human-designed)
- [ ] All functionality preserved
- [ ] Passes visual inspection (looks modern, not AI-generated)
